Micron Technology Inc said itexpects to record a net loss of about 11 mln dlrs in the secondquarter compared to a loss of 9.7 mln dlrs in the first quarterand 9.8 mln dlrs in the year-ago second quarter.    Revenues in the quarter ended March five increased to about20.4 mln dlrs from 18.8 mln in the preceeding quarter and 9.4mln dlrs in the year-ago quarter.    The company makes semiconductors, memory components andrelated products. Reuter&#3;